<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wolfram von Egloffstein</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Göldlein, Diener der Stadt, wegen der Gefangennahme des C. Behringersdorfer, Hintersasse des Ulrich Volland, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_154" id="76r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_154_r1l10">VVolfram vom Eglofſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_154_r1l11">. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> . 
    <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan></del> VVolfram / vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> <expan cert="unknown">C</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> pergerſt </del> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> volland </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l12">vnſer Burger . vvie Jr den . <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Pergerſtorffer der Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l13">von des walds wegen hie bey <expan>nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> gelegen der ſein kauffts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l14">gut ſey <expan>cʒuverſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſtee gefangen habt / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ J </del> ſenden vvir cʒu euch hanſen Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l16">mit ewch dauon cʒu reden / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . vvaʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l17">dyener etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ poſt Jacobi </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_154" id="76r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wolfram vom Eglofstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wolfram, uns hat
                            <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Volland, unser burger, wie ir den <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Pergerstorffer, der im von des walds wegen hie
                        bey <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> gelegen, der sein kauffts gut sey,
                            <expan>czu versprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> stee, gefangen habt.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> senden wir czu euch Hansen Göldlein,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener, mit ewch davon czu reden. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz der
                            <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dyener etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi post Jacobi.</ab>
</div>
